WEBVTT

00:00:40.159 --> 00:00:41.200
Mom

00:00:41.679 --> 00:00:42.840
From today on

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.479
I'll always be by your side

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.000
I'll protect you

00:00:48.359 --> 00:00:49.759
This eye of mine

00:00:51.320 --> 00:00:52.119
is blind now

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:55.039
Thanks to you

00:00:55.439 --> 00:00:56.200
You and me

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.079
We're done

00:01:21.879 --> 00:01:23.120
All the evidence on Long Xiao

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:24.519
is in that file bag.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:28.799
Print this stuff out,

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:31.519
and we can dig up who's backing Long Xiao.

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:43.040
This is my last resort.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.000
What now?

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:56.079
What's your bright idea this time?

00:01:57.439 --> 00:01:58.920
This bag has a film roll in it.

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:01.000
The film roll has Long Xiao's ledger on it.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Every single record.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.239
Long Xiao and his backers are the ones who hurt you.

00:02:04.239 --> 00:02:04.959
I'll avenge you.

00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:06.120
And get you justice.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.000
Fine, you don't have to believe me.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:10.879
See you tomorrow.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.759
Okay, I'll stay here with you tonight, Brother Hai.

00:02:13.759 --> 00:02:14.919
I'll stay too.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.360
No.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:19.199
Nobody enters this billiards hall today.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.919
But why, brother?

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.319
He's guarding against us, I guess.

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:26.879
Brother, you don't trust me?

00:02:27.199 --> 00:02:28.000
Dali.

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.360
I just want to be more careful with this.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:34.800
Zhu Yihai, who are you suspecting?

00:02:36.199 --> 00:02:36.719
Brother.

00:02:36.719 --> 00:02:37.520
Let's go.

00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:39.360
Just watch,

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.319
tomorrow some people will make up excuses,

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:43.360
saying the film roll got exposed or something.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:02.360
I'm leaving too.

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:35.120
Old bastard

00:03:36.639 --> 00:03:38.639
How the hell did you get in there?

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.479
At least this time,

00:03:43.759 --> 00:03:45.759
I held down Aimin Street for you.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:47.360
And another thing,

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.400
picking my mom? You've got taste.

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:51.520
Alright.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:27.160
Brother Hai

00:04:27.319 --> 00:04:27.959
Brother Hai

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.000
Brother Hai

00:04:40.759 --> 00:04:41.959
It's really broken

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:46.879
What are you staring at for so long?

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:48.480
Dali

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.240
Let's go, Brother Hai

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:51.800
Where to?

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:53.160
To hand over the evidence

00:04:58.439 --> 00:04:58.920
Wait

00:04:59.480 --> 00:05:00.519
What the hell happened?

00:05:01.839 --> 00:05:03.079
What do you think happened?

00:05:03.439 --> 00:05:05.319
He never had any evidence to begin with

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:06.920
No, yesterday at the billiards-

00:05:06.920 --> 00:05:10.519
Nobody came to the billiards hall yesterday

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:12.319
So you suspect me

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.519
How could I suspect you, Wei Wei?

00:05:15.120 --> 00:05:16.879
So you suspect me and Lili then

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:18.399
Dali

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:19.680
Enough

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:21.040
Zhu Yihai

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.759
Nobody's playing your games.

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:46.519
Mom

00:05:47.879 --> 00:05:48.720
All these years

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:50.360
my dad's been locked up in prison

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:51.560
Don't blame him

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:52.360
okay?

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:55.319
Out of all his women

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:59.480
you're the one who stuck with him to the end

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.480
I'm really happy about that

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:04.399
I think my mom

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:05.959
is incredibly cool

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:07.519
and has so much character

00:06:13.519 --> 00:06:14.519
Don't worry, Mom

00:06:15.079 --> 00:06:17.360
I've cleaned up all his messes for him

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:19.959
And I'd never follow in his footsteps

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:23.360
There's only one threat left around me now

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:26.600
and I'll take care of it for sure

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:29.040
Just you wait

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:01.319
Let's go for a walk.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.879
I used to come here a lot as a kid.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:11.879
I'd watch the trains pull out one by one,

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.360
and I'd wonder...

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:15.160
where they were all going.

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:18.399
Would I grow up to be like them,

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.959
traveling somewhere far away?

00:07:22.839 --> 00:07:23.879
But here I am now,

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:27.560
and I've never even left Night City.

00:07:34.319 --> 00:07:35.600
So why don't you go out and travel?

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:39.439
Look at them.

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:42.560
Just like these abandoned trains,

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:45.800
at some point, who knows when,

00:07:48.319 --> 00:07:49.560
they just stopped running.

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:51.639
This old platform...

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:53.040
is their home forever.

00:07:56.879 --> 00:07:57.959
They can't run anymore,

00:07:59.519 --> 00:08:02.079
maybe because they miss the old days.

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:04.480
Guohong Factory doesn't smelt steel anymore,

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:07.240
but that doesn't mean it's lost its meaning.

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:11.480
But they're already broken down.

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:14.040
Other than here,

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:15.920
where else could they go?

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:18.040
Have you ever thought,

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:19.439
maybe they're not broken,

00:08:20.079 --> 00:08:21.519
they're just stuck in the past,

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:23.319
trapped there.

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:29.959
Zhu Yihai, what are you getting at?

00:08:32.759 --> 00:08:35.000
You told Long Xiao about the video hall, didn't you?

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:37.679
And you leaked Huilian's whereabouts too.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.240
You destroyed the film roll

00:08:40.679 --> 00:08:43.159
so I couldn't find out who's behind Long Xiao.

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.120
Did you know,

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:46.960
Dali and Wei Wei showed up just to find you.

00:08:47.759 --> 00:08:48.559
Wei Wei...

00:08:49.039 --> 00:08:50.879
About your eye...

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:51.879
I'm sorry.

00:08:52.639 --> 00:08:53.600
That's boring.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:55.279
Isn't it kind of cool?

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:58.600
I've still got the other one, right?

00:09:01.279 --> 00:09:02.080
Brother Hai,

00:09:03.759 --> 00:09:05.000
I believe you.

00:09:05.919 --> 00:09:08.080
Everything you've done,

00:09:08.399 --> 00:09:09.960
I can understand it all.

00:09:11.159 --> 00:09:13.159
Don't ever bring this up again.

00:09:13.159 --> 00:09:14.519
Mention it again and I'm done with you.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:19.200
But Huilian's whereabouts...

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.759
only a few of us knew about that.

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:23.639
There's a mole among us.

00:09:25.879 --> 00:09:27.039
But you've gotta help me put on a show.

00:09:27.919 --> 00:09:28.879
Too late, Zhu Yihai.

00:09:29.639 --> 00:09:30.399
You and me,

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.159
we're done.

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:35.120
Nobody enters this billiards hall today.

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:36.399
He's guarding against us, I guess.

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:37.799
Just watch,

00:09:37.799 --> 00:09:40.200
tomorrow some people will make up excuses,

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.879
saying the film roll got exposed or something.

00:09:42.840 --> 00:09:43.759
I'm leaving too.

00:09:54.279 --> 00:09:55.440
Who would've thought

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:58.679
Lili, with that honest face, was actually a spy

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:00.720
Good thing Dahai was prepared

00:10:02.639 --> 00:10:03.440
Zhu Yihai

00:10:04.840 --> 00:10:06.639
You actually set a trap to deceive me

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:09.559
You guarded against me like you would Long Xiao

00:10:10.519 --> 00:10:11.720
Here at Dahai Billiards Hall

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:14.039
I, Qiao Lili, will always be an outsider, right?

00:10:14.919 --> 00:10:15.720
Then what about me?

00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:17.320
Screw you

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:18.919
Our Huilian

00:10:18.919 --> 00:10:21.399
became sworn siblings with Zhu Yihai right here

00:10:21.840 --> 00:10:23.080
Each of them got a little necklace

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.720
with the word "loyalty" on it

00:10:24.919 --> 00:10:26.320
Acting like it's the real deal

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:28.039
Do you have one?

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:29.519
No, I don't

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:32.519
I just wanted to help you

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.320
I just wanted to tell you

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.279
that it's not only Qian Huilian and Wei Wei who can help you

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:37.720
I, Qiao Lili, can too

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:43.879
Yes

00:10:46.759 --> 00:10:47.759
I was wrong

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:51.120
I never thought he could be so cruel

00:10:51.639 --> 00:10:53.120
And I never thought

00:10:53.639 --> 00:10:55.639
I'd become a traitor to you all

00:10:56.639 --> 00:10:59.399
When I watched him brutalize Wei Wei

00:10:59.399 --> 00:11:01.000
do you think my heart wasn't aching?

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:05.000
But I just wanted to help you

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:07.240
to do something for you

00:11:08.399 --> 00:11:09.240
That's all

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.720
I know I'm pathetic

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.440
After you all got hurt

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.080
I've been laughing at myself every single day

00:11:19.519 --> 00:11:20.720
I laugh at myself

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:22.720
for not being able to do even one thing right

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:24.600
I'm just useless

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:26.879
Lili, you're not useless

00:11:26.879 --> 00:11:29.320
Everything you've done means the world to me

00:11:29.799 --> 00:11:31.200
Lili, you know what?

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:32.399
Ever since I was little

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:33.600
no one ever loved me

00:11:34.039 --> 00:11:35.080
No one cared about me

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:37.960
You're the first person in this world to care for me

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:40.240
Do you remember when I just got out of the hospital

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:42.000
and you helped me pack my clothes?

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:47.039
From that day on

00:11:47.039 --> 00:11:48.039
I knew for sure

00:11:48.519 --> 00:11:50.120
that you'd be the most important person to me

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:52.240
Zhu Yihai, do you take me for a fool?

00:11:53.559 --> 00:11:56.440
I heard your whole conversation with Qian Huilian at the hospital

00:11:56.759 --> 00:11:57.720
She's the most important one to you

00:11:57.720 --> 00:11:58.559
Not me

00:11:58.559 --> 00:12:00.000
Everything I'm saying is true

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:02.159
I had no family growing up

00:12:02.159 --> 00:12:03.879
No friends, no one who cared about me

00:12:04.519 --> 00:12:05.759
Only you cared about me

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:11.120
I'm not Zhu Yihai

00:12:12.120 --> 00:12:13.440
I'm Zhu Chaoyang